Kisuaheli / Nachrichten (Jürgen Hasselmann 28.11.1999)

Sauti ya Ujerumani:  Idhaa ya Kiswahili - Habari

(Keywords = Swahili, Deutsche, Welle, Radio,

Broadcasting, Media, Audio, Radio, Redio, RealPlayer, Realaudio,

